Welcome to
Arbor Investment Management, LLC

Arbor Investment Management, LLC helps clients achieve their financial goals with comprehensive, 
personalized wealth management strategies and state-of-the-art retirement planning.
We believe creating a personalized strategy and constructing tailored portfolios 
that match the unique financial goals of each client is the most effective way to build wealth and 
secure long-term financial stability for our clients. Our valuation based, long-term approach to 
investment management is key to successfully navigating our clients’ investment portfolios through 
the investment life cycle of accumulation, retirement transition, and wealth preservation.
As a private Registered Investment Advisory Firm our fiduciary responsibility 
to put our clients’ interests first is paramount, and we pride ourselves on being tireless 
advocates for the specific financial goals and plans of our clients.
At heart, long-term financial planning and investing is about securing the 
financial independence that allows you to provide consistently for your family and enjoy the 
lifestyle you desire, both before and after retirement. At Arbor, we understand these basic 
underlying goals and all our activities are structured around achieving them for each client 
family. We believe our personal and professional success as investment managers is earned by 
being a trusted long-term partner in your financial success story. We invite you to please 
Contact Us to learn more about our services.


