Our Firm

Arbor Investment Management is an Independent Registered Investment Advisor, which means 
we are not biased by any in-house products or tied to any brokerage or insurance firm’s 
investment products. Instead, we are beholden only to the expectations and goals of 
the clients who hire us, and are free to use the widest array of investments to deliver 
on those goals. As a Registered Investment Advisory firm we have a fiduciary 
responsibility to put the interests of our clients first. Our culture at Arbor is 
focused on exceeding our clients’ expectations while maintaining the highest standards 
in meeting our ethical and professional responsibilities.
Our services are designed for mid to high net worth individuals 
and families with a long-term financial perspective who are seeking a competent, 
trusted advisor. Arbor Investment Management provides comprehensive, personalized 
wealth management and retirement planning for its clients. By taking the time to 
fully understand the unique financial situation, investment time horizons, and risk 
tolerance of each client, we are able to construct and manage investment portfolios 
tailored to deliver on each client's personal long-term goals.
Our expertise is helping each client get their financial house 
in order and keep it that way the rest of their lives. Whatever your investment 
management needs, the dedicated portfolio managers and support staff personnel 
at Arbor Investment Management are ready to get started on the process of 
building a successful long-term partnership with you.









